title: Nonstop Rudy, Fecal Felon 1.27.20

description:
In episode 556, Jack and Miles are joined by comic artist Kim Winder to discuss Lev Parnas being younger than Jared Leto, impeachment updates, Pete Buttigieg defending himself, a potential New Orleans Saints cover up, a mystery pooper being caught, and more!

FOOTNOTES:

  1. Lev Parnas is somehow younger than Jared Leto
  2. 'Take her out': Recording appears to capture Trump at private dinner saying he wants Ukraine ambassador fired
  3. Trump’s Team Warns GOP Senators: Vote Against Him, And Their ‘Head Will Be On A Pike’ — Report
  4. 'Vote against the president, and your head will be on a pike': GOP Senators 'are warned' not to break ranks with Trump in impeachment vote
  5. Trump’s Mad His Lawyers Have To Defend Him When TV Ratings Are Low
  6. ‘Bulls---’: Buttigieg chafes at criticism over McKinsey work
  7. Pete Buttigieg
  8. Bakers, grocers involved in 16-year price-fixing conspiracy: Competition Bureau
  9. How Mayor Pete's consulting work for Loblaws brought the Canadian bread price-fixing scandal to Democratic primary
  10. Pete Buttigieg Denies Involvement With Canada's Bread Price-Fixing Scandal
  11. NFL’s Saints seek to shield PR help to church in sex crisis
  12. MASSACHUSETTS WOMAN ALLEGED PARKING LOT POOPER ... Busted By Cops
  13. WATCH: Andy Shauf - "Neon Skyline"
